<blockquote class="blockquote-center">
I heard the echo, <span class="label default">from the valleys and the heart</span>
Open to the lonely soul of <span class="label info">sickle harvesting</span>
Repeat outrightly, but also repeat the well-being of
Eventually <span class="label warning">swaying in the desert oasis</span>
<span class="label success">I believe</span> I am
<span class="label primary">Born as the bright summer flowers</span>
Do not withered undefeated fiery demon rule
Heart rate and breathing to bear <span class="label danger">the load of the cumbersome</span>
Bored
</blockquote>

